  <brief_title>Consumption of Potatoes, Avocados and Chickpeas and Cognitive Function in Older Adults</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Consumption of Potatoes, Avocados and Chickpeas Daily for 6 Months on Cognitive Function in Older Adults</official_title>
